1. Ova *misterija* još nije razrešena. (This *mystery* is still unsolved.)
2. Knjiga je prepuna *misterija*. (The book is full of *mysteries*.)
3. Uzbudljivo je pratiti rješavanje *misterije*. (It's exciting to follow the solving of a *mystery*.)
4. Policija istražuje *misteriozne* okolnosti smrti. (The police are investigating *mysterious* circumstances of death.)
5. Tajanstvena osoba sa maskom stvorila je *misteriju* u gradu. (A mysterious person wearing a mask created a *mystery* in the city.)
6. Ona je pravi stručnjak za *misteriozne* slučajeve. (She is a real expert in *mysterious* cases.)
7. *Misteriozna* suma novca pronađena je u sefu. (A *mysterious* sum of money was found in the safe.)
8. Ovo je pravi slučaj za *misterijske* romane. (This is a real case for *mystery* novels.)
9. Glavni lik pokušava razriješiti *misteriju* prije nego što bude prekasno. (The main character tries to solve the *mystery* before it's too late.)
10. Film je prepun *misterioznih* obrata i iznenađenja. (The movie is full of *mysterious* twists and surprises.)